Global Ricinus Communis Seed Oil Market Insights
Ricinus Communis Seed Oil Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Ricinus Communis Seed Oil Market Overview
The global Ricinus Communis Seed Oil market has been experiencing steady growth, valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2023, and it is projected to reach around USD 1.8 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 8% during the forecast period. This increase is driven by the rising demand for natural skincare and hair care products, along with its use in the pharmaceutical industry. The market expansion is further supported by increased awareness of its benefits and its wide application in cosmetics, personal care, and industrial uses.

